      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Cemetery Office ¶ Brighton May 31st 1862 ¶ Dr Mueller ¶ Government Botanist ¶ Sir,...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">62.05.31</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Samuel<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Simmonds</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Minute book, Trustees of the Brighton General Cemetery,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Melbourne,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>p. 80<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found; MS is a version copied into the minutes.</p>
               </note>Cemetery Office</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Brighton May 31st 1862</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Dr Mueller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Government Botanist</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am instructed by the Trustees of the "Brighton General Cemetery" to make application, requesting you to favor them by granting them such Trees &amp; Shrubs as you may be enabled, in order that, with them, they might improve the appearance of the Cemetery for which they are Trustees.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Cemetery has for a considerable period been in a very neglected condition, owing to the Trustees not having Funds at their disposal for improving it. They feel however that they must make some effort<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">now</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>towards improving its appearance, and trust you will aid them by acceding to their request with your usual liberality evinced towards all Public Institutions.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>At the meeting of the Trustees on 30 May 1862,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the proposal was put 'That in the event of Dr Mueller declining to accede to the request of the Trustees, the Secretary be instructed to expend the sum of Three Pounds (£3)<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>on Trees &amp; Shrubs' (p. 80). M agreed to the request;<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>see M to S. Simmonds, 2 June 1862<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(in this edition as 62-06-02c).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your most obedient Servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>S. P. Simmonds</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Secretary</p>
         </div>
